Roles and Responsibilities:

Design and produce graphics, online banners, storyboards, website layouts and animated infographics
Develop after effects for video production 


Job Requirement:

Degree/Diploma/ Certificate in Graphic Design or related disciplines;
Minimum 5 years graphic design experience preferred;
Self motivated, responsible, mature and able to handle multiple projects independently;
Proficiency in PC, experience in using Photoshop, Illustrator, Indesign and After Effect etc.;
Good presentation skill and strong creativity;
Able to work under pressure, meet tight deadline and willing to work overtime if needed;
Drawing skill is an advantage;
Knowledge in video shooting, recording, editing & post-production for all kinds of video is an advantage;
5.5 days’ work per week

Interested parties please click “Apply Now" to submit your complete resume with compensation history, expected salary and REFERENCE NUMBER or by fax to 2798 2925.

We are an equal opportunity employer and welcome applications from all qualified candidates. Information provided will be treated in strict confidence and only be used for recruitment related purpose. Applicant who is not invited for an interview within 6 weeks may consider their application not successful. All personal data of unsuccessful applicants will be destroyed within 6 months.

Responsibilities:

Handle various design projects, mainly focusing on video editing and animation, visual and graphic artwork design
Edit video, effect composition, motion graphic and animations
Generate ideas and creative concepts for digital campaigns and social media posts
To draft both English and Chinese press and publication copies;
Managing social media platforms;
Other ad-hoc copywriting tasks required to facilitate various marketing activities;
Manage other ad hoc projects as assigned
Requirements:


Degree holder in Creative Media, Marketing, translation or relevant disciplines: communications, journalism or advertising;
Excellent knowledge of photography/videography within the digital domain;
Excel in Adobe Premiere and Adobe Photoshop;
Excellent command of written, spoken English, Mandarin, and Cantonese;
Familiar with various social media platforms;
Must possess outstanding proofreading skills;
Proficient in Microsoft Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and Chinese Word Processing;
Self-motivated and proactive team player with good communication skills.

Job Responsibilities:

Handle day to day graphics design for advertising, marketing, social media content;
Design and production for event decoration and promotional items;
Create concept and artwork as company branding;
any ad-hoc projects that maybe assigned by manager;

Job Requirement:

At least 3 years working experience in media, advertising agency preferred;
Diploma or above in in Art, Graphic Design, Multimedia or related disciplines in Graphic Design;    
Able to handle multiple tasks with tight schedule and work under pressure;
Detail-oriented, responsible, independent and can work in a team;
Relevant experience/ enthusiast in the automobile or eSport project is preferred;               
Proficient in Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator of Mac environment is a MUST;
Good command of written and spoken Cantonese and English;
Immediate availability is highly preferred

Interested candidates, please send your full resume stating with contact details, current & expected salary email to HR Department. 

All applications will be treated in strict confidence and be used solely for recruitment purpose.

The Role
We are looking for a creative and passionate Graphic Designer to join our team.  You will have a chance to work at a fast-paced mission driven company that brings material science to life and benefit the mass.  We are bringing business disruption and new hygiene standard to the world with the introduction of new photocatalyst products and services. With the continuous R&D and business innovation, we are thrilled to develop the next generation technology that safeguards everyday life.  Raze Technology is the world's leading photocatalyst solution company, developing a long-lasting disinfectant coating.

Responsibilities
Responsible for creative concept development and handle all stages of design include but not limited to the following: 


Social media visual and feed designs (Facebook, Instagram, eDM, Google ad, etc.); 
Online store visual (Web banner, product page, etc); 
Sales kit and POP materials;
Product retouching and mock-ups; 
Perform ad-hoc projects as assigned.

Requirements


Diploma or above in Graphic Design/ Multimedia/ Creative Media or other related disciplines;
At least 3 years relevant working experience in graphic design, FMCG or digital marketing agency experience is preferred;
Proficient in using Adobe Illustrator, Photoshop in Mac environment; 
Proficient in animation and video editing is a plus;
Good team player, multi-tasking and responsible;
Visual merchandising experience is an advantage; 
Immediate availability is highly preferable.

We offer the right candidate attractive remuneration package and outstanding prospects for career advancement and development.  The right candidate will progress career in a forward thinking and dynamic business with exciting growth plans.  If you are qualified and interested, please send your full resume with current & expected salary and availability by clicking "APPLY".

All information collected will be treated as strictly confidential and used for recruitment purposes only. (Only shortlisted candidates will be notified)

Responsibilities:


